// Default accounts config for Authenticator
// Copy this file to accounts.json and edit with your real secrets.
// On first visit (empty localStorage), the app loads accounts.json automatically.
//
// Comments: lines starting with // or # are stripped before parsing.
//
// Fields:
//   name      - Account name / label (required)
//   issuer    - Service provider, e.g. "GitHub" (optional, recommended)
//   secret    - Base32-encoded TOTP secret (required)
//   algorithm - SHA-1, SHA-256, or SHA-512 (default: SHA-1)
//   period    - Time step in seconds: 30, 60, 300, 3600, 86400 (default: 30)
//   digits    - Code length: 6 or 8 (default: 6)
//   url       - Optional link shown on the account name
